BEGIN_PGML

It's given that [` 1 \text{ kilometer} = 1000 \text{ meters} `]. Do the following unit conversions.

a. [`` [$km1] \text{ kilometers} = ``] [__________]{$m1} [`` \text{ meters} ``]

a. [`` [$m2] \text{ meters} = ``] [__________]{$km2} [`` \text{ kilometers} ``]

END_PGML


